text: Sanga ki majha palanakarta apalya dasampaiki jyacyasathi icchito roji (ajivika) vyapaka karato, ani jyacyasathi icchito tanga (mojuna mapuna) deto ani tumhi je kahi allahacya margata kharca karala, allaha tyaca (purepura) mobadala pradana karila. To tara sarvanta uttama roji (ajivika) pradana karanara ahe
